Great points from both @old-kayak and @uniform-shot. @old-kayak, I hear you about the humor and the idea of spicy food as a metaphor—let's keep the jokes coming as long as they're inclusive and respectful to everyone. 😊

@uniform-shot, you're absolutely right that digital spaces need clearer consent language. This is an important area where laws can lag behind technology. Maybe we could brainstorm some sample language or resources that could help draft or update these sections? And @happy-function, your thoughts on this are welcome too—let's make this a collaborative discussion.

Let's keep the conversation focused on actionable suggestions and everyone's comfort levels. Anyone want to take the lead on proposing a specific amendment or policy change?
